statements: SELECT * FROM performance_metrics_nn_models
SELECT model_name, dataset_name, accuracy FROM performance_metrics_nn_models
SELECT training_loss, validation_loss FROM performance_metrics_nn_models WHERE accuracy > 0.8
SELECT * FROM performance_metrics_nn_models WHERE dataset_name = 'CIFAR-10'
SELECT model_name, accuracy FROM performance_metrics_nn_models ORDER BY accuracy DESC
SELECT model_id, model_name, training_loss FROM performance_metrics_nn_models WHERE accuracy > 0.9 ORDER BY training_loss DESC
SELECT model_name, dataset_name, validation_loss FROM performance_metrics_nn_models WHERE dataset_name = 'CIFAR-10' ORDER BY validation_loss ASC
SELECT model_name, dataset_name, validation_loss, accuracy FROM performance_metrics_nn_models WHERE training_loss < 0.05 AND validation_loss < 0.1 ORDER BY accuracy DESC
SELECT model_name, dataset_name, accuracy FROM performance_metrics_nn_models WHERE accuracy BETWEEN 0.8 AND 0.9 ORDER BY dataset_name, accuracy DESC
SELECT * FROM performance_metrics_nn_models WHERE model_id IN (1, 3, 5, 7) ORDER BY model_id ASC
SELECT * FROM ModelPerformanceMetrics WHERE model_id = 1;
SELECT model_id, training_loss, validation_loss FROM ModelPerformanceMetrics WHERE epoch > 5;
SELECT model_id, training_loss, validation_loss FROM ModelPerformanceMetrics WHERE accuracy > 0.9 ORDER BY model_id DESC;
SELECT model_id, training_loss, validation_loss, accuracy FROM ModelPerformanceMetrics WHERE validation_loss < 0.5 ORDER BY accuracy DESC;
SELECT model_id, epoch, training_loss, validation_loss, accuracy FROM ModelPerformanceMetrics WHERE model_id IN (2, 3);
SELECT model_id, epoch, training_loss, validation_loss, accuracy FROM ModelPerformanceMetrics ORDER BY model_id DESC, epoch ASC LIMIT 5
SELECT * FROM ModelPerformanceMetrics WHERE accuracy > 0.8 ORDER BY accuracy DESC LIMIT 5

SELECT model_id, AVG(training_loss) AS avg_training_loss, AVG(validation_loss) AS avg_validation_loss FROM ModelPerformanceMetrics GROUP BY model_id HAVING AVG(training_loss) > 0.5 AND AVG(validation_loss) < 0.2

SELECT ModelPerformanceMetrics.model_id, training_loss, validation_loss, learning_rate FROM ModelPerformanceMetrics JOIN ModelTrainingHistory ON ModelPerformanceMetrics.model_id = ModelTrainingHistory.model_id AND ModelPerformanceMetrics.epoch = ModelTrainingHistory.epoch
SELECT model_id, COUNT(*) AS training_epochs FROM ModelPerformanceMetrics GROUP BY model_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 3 ORDER BY training_epochs DESC
SELECT * FROM neural_network_models;
SELECT model_name, performance_metrics FROM neural_network_models;
SELECT model_name, performance_metrics FROM neural_network_models WHERE model_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT * FROM training_data ORDER BY training_loss DESC;
SELECT model_id, batch_size FROM hyperparameters WHERE learning_rate > 0.01;
SELECT model_name, performance_metrics FROM neural_network_models;
SELECT data_id, training_loss, validation_accuracy FROM training_data WHERE validation_accuracy > 0.9;
SELECT model_id, learning_rate, batch_size FROM hyperparameters WHERE learning_rate > 0.001 AND batch_size <= 32;
SELECT model_name, performance_metrics FROM neural_network_models ORDER BY model_name DESC;
SELECT model_name, performance_metrics FROM neural_network_models WHERE model_name ILIKE 'R%';
SELECT * FROM neural_network_models;
SELECT model_id, model_name, accuracy FROM neural_network_models ORDER BY accuracy DESC;
SELECT model_name, accuracy, loss FROM neural_network_models WHERE loss > 0.2;
SELECT model_id, model_name, accuracy, loss FROM neural_network_models WHERE accuracy > 0.8 AND loss < 0.1;
SELECT model_id, model_name, accuracy FROM neural_network_models WHERE accuracy BETWEEN 0.7 AND 0.9 ORDER BY accuracy DESC;
SELECT * FROM neural_network_models;
SELECT model_name, accuracy FROM neural_network_models WHERE accuracy > 0.9;
SELECT dataset_name, model_name FROM training_data td JOIN neural_network_models nnm ON td.model_id = nnm.model_id;
SELECT model_name, learning_rate, batch_size FROM neural_network_models nnm JOIN hyperparameters hp ON nnm.model_id = hp.model_id;
SELECT model_name, precision, recall FROM neural_network_models nnm JOIN evaluation_metrics em ON nnm.model_id = em.model_id WHERE precision > 0.8 AND recall > 0.7;
SELECT * FROM performance_metrics;
SELECT model_name, training_accuracy, test_accuracy FROM performance_metrics;
SELECT model_name, training_accuracy, test_accuracy FROM performance_metrics ORDER BY model_name ASC;
SELECT model_name, training_accuracy, test_accuracy FROM performance_metrics WHERE training_accuracy > 0.8;
SELECT model_name, training_accuracy, test_accuracy FROM performance_metrics WHERE test_accuracy < 0.7;
SELECT model_name, training_accuracy, test_accuracy FROM performance_metrics WHERE training_accuracy > 0.8 ORDER BY test_accuracy DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT model_name, architecture, optimizer FROM performance_metrics INNER JOIN model_details ON performance_metrics.model_id = model_details.model_id WHERE model_details.learning_rate > 0.001 ORDER BY model_name ASC LIMIT 5;

SELECT model_name, epoch, loss FROM performance_metrics INNER JOIN training_data ON performance_metrics.model_id = training_data.model_id WHERE training_data.accuracy > 0.9 ORDER BY epoch DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT model_name, accuracy, batch_size FROM performance_metrics INNER JOIN hyperparameters ON performance_metrics.model_id = hyperparameters.model_id WHERE hyperparameters.epochs = 20 ORDER BY accuracy DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT model_name, epoch, loss FROM performance_metrics INNER JOIN test_data ON performance_metrics.model_id = test_data.model_id WHERE test_data.loss < 0.1 ORDER BY epoch ASC LIMIT 5;
